Isabel Jeans https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Isabel_Jeans 0 Isabel Jeans (16 September 1891 – 4 September 1985) was an English stage and film actress known for her roles in several Alfred Hitchcock films and her portrayal of Aunt Alicia in the 1958 musical film Gigi, among others.
